room_title: Escape room "Dracula" by Quest Factor in Seattle
room_description: You are adventurers who discovered vampire crypt. The front door slammed shut behind you and unfortunately, your group got trapped inside... Soon the dead man will rise from the grave and feast on your blood ... The only chance for salvation is to catch the vampire by surprise and kill sleeping demon once and for all. But you need to hurry, only one hour left before sunset!
